{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2089335, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 406648, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "因为市场经济", "timestamp": 1626587255, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2089336, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 406648, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "赚自己的钱 让别人说去吧", "timestamp": 1626587277, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2089337, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 406648, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不如dz从劳动价值论论证一下金融有没有创造价值，还是仅仅是转移价值?", "timestamp": 1626587281, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2089341, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 406648, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "学过不少金融的课，感觉有些金融领域的\"知识\"、\"技巧\"，完全是在金融人自己构建的\"场域\"内使用，外部性一般", "timestamp": 1626587334, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2089347, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 406648, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "金融初衷是好的，但是很多人在上面投机，套利这种行为有任何外部性么", "timestamp": 1626587398, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2089353, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 406648, "reply_to": 2089347, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 我觉得很多投机是二级市场的东西，而且说白了股票基金这种市场本来就有巨大的风险性和各种内部交易的可能性存在，那些投资者应该在投资之前就明白风险性的存在", "timestamp": 1626587462, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2089356, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 406648, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "装什么装啊", "timestamp": 1626587504, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2089358, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 406648, "reply_to": 2089356, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 酸什么酸啊😅", "timestamp": 1626587533, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2089359, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 406648, "reply_to": 2089353, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 割韭菜理直气壮冠冕堂皇，仌！🤗 ", "timestamp": 1626587538, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2089370, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 406648, "reply_to": 2089353, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 不是你跟他说了有风险就可以随意割韭菜了，普通人获得的信息都是非常有限的，很多时候这些机构利用不对称的信息割韭菜，这种行为对整个社会有什么帮助呢？", "timestamp": 1626587641, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2089387, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 406648, "reply_to": 2089358, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 急了是吧😅搞钱就说搞钱，忽悠谁呢？", "timestamp": 1626587928, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2089421, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 406648, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "说白了这些非共产主义的东西总会被消灭的，历史会评价金融的价值。", "timestamp": 1626588397, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2089425, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 406648, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "一群人拿着非他人领域的知识和既定现状摆出一副真理的模样恶不恶心。", "timestamp": 1626588460, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2089430, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 406648, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "确实", "timestamp": 1626588634, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2089452, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 406648, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "一群赚不到钱的穷比只能拿社会价值安慰自己😅", "timestamp": 1626588910, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2089460, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 406648, "reply_to": 2089452, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 大哥 还是您🎣水平高", "timestamp": 1626589079, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2089474, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 406648, "reply_to": 2089452, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 高手，可惜爷家里有钱", "timestamp": 1626589266, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2089479, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "nam